# Backend Migration & Segmentation Refactor Plan

## Goal
Shift the image processing pipeline from the frontend (Android Native Module) to the backend (Python/OpenCV). The goal is to perform true flood-fill region extraction with vector contour generation (`findContours` + `approxPolyDP`) on the backend, converting the React Native frontend into a pure high-performance rendering engine using Skia and Reanimated.

